'''Bonecrushers''' were [[Wikipedia:Tyrannosaur|Tyrannosaur]]-like creatures native to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Dandrian]]. They could grow to about the same size as an adult [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] and had gaping maws filled with sharp teeth. [[Sti Groon]] had a Bonecrusher which he used as his champion in gladiatorial challenges whenever people couldn't afford to pay him for information.<ref name="Dandrian's Ring">''{{ChallengeCite|49|Dandrian's Ring (adventure)}}''</ref>

